Method Detail

addMapping

protected abstract void addMapping(java.lang.String line)
Add mapping(s) for a line from the literalFile. Extractions will hold a StringExtractionData whose string is the mapping value for literal keys that match.

Implementers should call addMapping(key, value).

getMapping

protected final java.lang.String getMapping(java.lang.String key)
Get the value for the given key.

NOTE: The normalizer will be applied to the key.

extract

public java.util.List<Extraction> extract(DocText docText,
                                          java.util.concurrent.atomic.AtomicBoolean die)
Perform the extraction on the doc text.

Parameters:
docText - The docText to extract from.
die - Trigger to halt processing. Needs to be monitored and obeyed; but can also be set from within the implementation. Use with care!
Returns:
one or more extractions or null.
